I know, everyone has heard this a thousand times, but in this case... I just find it down right hilarious. I&#039;m not even mad I lost. I&#039;m mid silver, so I&#039;m no star player by any stretch of the imagination, but when I come across a game so wildly unreasonable, I do start to ask myself.... &quot;is Rito just pulling summoner names out of a hat for these games?&quot;

I won&#039;t bore you guys with the details, but I do want to ask how a person in their provisionals for the first time ever, loses six games, and gets carried in one, manages to get put as my mid laner during my promos xd (wait, he was silver in season 3 some how lol, but hasn&#039;t played since then)

not only that i had an ADC riven and a yolo top lane fiora xd. the real crime was our soraka was a great support main, and i feel bad she was subjected to that shitfest of a game{{sticker:sg-soraka}}
